<HR><H2>
Geometry Research Groups
</H2>
This page collects pointers to home pages of research groups working in
discrete and computational geometry or related areas.

<UL>
<LI> <A HREF="http://iamwww.unibe.ch/~fcglib/index.html">
     U. Bern, Forschungsgruppe Computergeometrie</A>

